Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:05.12,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,A radiation machine gave\None patient
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:07.28,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,roughly a hundred times\Nthe intended dose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:10.34,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The manufacturer said it\Nwas impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:12.10,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Then it happened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:14.54,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The Therac twenty-five\Nreplaced physical
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:17.56,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,safety interlocks with\Nsoftware checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:21.28,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,During fast data entry, a\Nrace condition
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:23.86,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,could leave the machine in\Nthe wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.44,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,state and fire a\Nfull-power beam with
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:27.61,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,no filter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:28.78,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Nobody caught it because\Nthe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:31.15,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,code had been reused from\Nolder machines,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:33.30,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,and reused code felt like\Ntested code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:35.55,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Operators reported errors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:36.85,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:39.52,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,manufacturer insisted the\Nmachine was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:40.65,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:41.78,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,More patients were burned\Nbefore the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:43.15,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,pattern was treated as\Nreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:46.22,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The disaster was not just\Nbad code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:49.02,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It was a system with no\Nindependent
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:51.23,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,safety layer, no quick way\Nto believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.72,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,field reports, and no\Ndesign for software
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.51,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,being wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:57.30,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,That is how small causes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:00:59.41,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,become massive\Nconsequences.
